<article class="container">
  <h1 id='title'>Ember multiselect-checkboxes demo</h1>

  <p>Documentation for this component is available
    <a href="https://github.com/rsschermer/ember-multiselect-checkboxes">here</a>.
  </p>

  <p>The source for this demo is available
    <a href="https://github.com/rsschermer/ember-multiselect-checkboxes/tree/gh-pages/demo-app">here</a>.
  </p>

  <section>
    <h2>Array of primitives</h2>

    <p>This example uses a plain javascript array as the selection options, with no label property specified:</p>

    <p>{{multiselect-checkboxes options=fruits selection=selectedFruits}}</p>

    <p>Selected fruits:
      <ul>
        {{#each selectedFruits as |fruit|}}
          <li>{{fruit}}</li>
        {{/each}}
      </ul>
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Array of plain js objects</h2>

    <p>This example uses an array of plain javascript objects as the selection options, with 'make' specified as the
      label property:
    </p>

    <p>{{multiselect-checkboxes options=cars selection=selectedCars labelProperty="make"}}</p>

    <p>Selected cars:
      <ul>
        {{#each selectedCars as |car|}}
          <li>make: {{car.make}}, color: {{car.color}}</li>
        {{/each}}
      </ul>
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Array of Ember objects</h2>

    <p>This example uses an array of ember objects as the selection options, with 'name' specified as the
      label property:
    </p>

    <p>{{multiselect-checkboxes options=persons selection=selectedPersons labelProperty="name"}}</p>

    <p>Selected persons:
      <ul>
        {{#each selectedPersons as |person|}}
          <li>name: {{person.name}}, gender: {{person.gender}}</li>
        {{/each}}
      </ul>
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Select/Unselect all</h2>

    <p>This example uses a plain javascript array as the selection options, "Select all/Unselect all feature":
    </p>

    <p>{{multiselect-checkboxes options=phones selection=selectedPhones}}</p>

    <p>
      <button {{action 'selectAllPhones'}}>Select all</button>
      <button {{action 'deselectAllPhones'}}>Deselect all</button>
    </p>

    <p>Selected phones:
      <ul>
        {{#each selectedPhones as |phone|}}
          <li>{{phone}}</li>
        {{/each}}
      </ul>
    </p>
  </section>

</article>
